  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so-- and then she began to-- she began to realize that, that I don't try to-- to boast or anything, but-- but she began to discover that the experience and the knowledge that I had-- after all, I was a co-editor of the newspaper and 13 years experience in the class struggle in Canada, and in the party where I could tell so much.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But-- but I just gave-- gave her in-- in small-- small doses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and then she-- she began to-- she began to ease up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then speaking about Canada, and that's-- that's in the book, when I spoke to her about Canada, told her about Canadian prairies and the beautiful wonders.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we never-- we never asked that, not these kind of things, how or where you trained, what-- what have you learned and so on, or if you had partial training.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We never talked about the inside-- inside being the-- there was plenty-- plenty else to talk about.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She-- no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is-- she-- she didn't tell me about all of that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The only-- only-- only very vague remarks here and there, as we went along.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the way you-- we just had to cover or cover up our past, you see?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In interrogation, you never-- and these things happen, tragic things happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And just a mistaken word in the interrogation when they caught you, and then they-- then you were finished.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they started to work on it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they beat it out-- out from you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So what intimate things did you-- did you go through with her?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What kind of conversations, private conversations did you talk about?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, all-- all about-- all about the-- the beauties, natural beauties of the-- of the tropical land.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
